[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Kit works best for brand new projects, when you\'re working from scratch. Once your code base evolves, managing updates and changes across specs become quite messy. It\'s not ideal for ongoing development. But, that\'s where Open Spec'

[00:51] [scene:talk]
